				<p>Another element that determines the ideal orientation of the building is the wind. If it is known that there are prevailing winds in other directions, taking advantage of them for cooling the house with natural ventilation would be a good idea. Therefore, when thinking the building’s orientation, it is essential to think how to manage the solar radiation and wind.</p>
